== Births == * {{ill|Kashō|ja|嘉祥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[850]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Seiwa|ja|正和天皇|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 56th Emperor of Japan (died [[880]]). * [[Keichō]] 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1604]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsudaira Naomoto|ja|松平直基|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the Echizen, Ōno, Yamagata, and Himeji Domains (died [[1648]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1844]] {{ill|May 12|ja|5月12日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Unii Ryūo|ja|雲井龍雄|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military official and politician from the Yonezawa Domain (died [[1870]]). * 明治2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1869]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Inoue Junosuke|ja|井上準之助|12=draft|12=draft}}, a politician (died [[1932]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1872]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Higuchi Ichiyō|ja|樋口一葉|12=draft|12=draft}}, a novelist and waka poet (died [[1896]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Taika|ja|大化|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[649]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Soga Kurayamada Ishikawa Maro|ja|蘇我倉山田石川麻呂|12=draft|12=draft}}, a noble and grandson of {{ill|Soga Umako|ja|蘇我馬子|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Meio|ja|明応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1499]] {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Rennyo|ja|蓮如|12=draft|12=draft}}, the founder of Jōdo Shinshū (born [[1415]]).
