* {{ill|Meio|ja|明応|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1499]] {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Rennyo|ja|蓮如|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the founder of Jōdo Shinshū (born [[1415]]).


