{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=三月廿五|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 3월 25일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 25''' is the 25th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Anwa|ja|安和|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Anwa|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[969]] {{ill|April 14|ja|4月14日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 14|qq=}}) – In the incident known as {{ill|Anwa no Hen|ja|安和の変|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Anwa no Hen|qq=}}, due to a denunciation by Genmanaka, 【Minamoto Takamasa】 (源高明) conspired to depose Crown Prince Morihei (守平親王) and was demoted to the Rank of 【Dazaiken-sui|大宰権帥】; this marked the establishment of the Fujiwara regency. * {{ill|Tenroku|ja|天禄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenroku|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[970]] {{ill|May 3|ja|5月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 3|qq=}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Anwa|ja|安和|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Anwa|qq=}} to {{ill|Tenroku|ja|天禄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenroku|qq=}}. * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1356]] {{ill|April 26|ja|4月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 26|qq=}}) – Nijō Yoshimoto compiled Japan’s first renga anthology, the {{ill|Utsubunashū|ja|菟玖波集|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Utsubunashū|qq=}}. * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1826]] {{ill|May 1|ja|5月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 1|qq=}}) – {{ill|Philip Franz von Siebold|ja|シーボルト|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Philip Franz von Siebold|qq=}}, while accompanying the head of the Dutch trading post, attempted to export Japanese maps and other prohibited items, and was subsequently expelled. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1870]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}}) – Surveying for Japan’s first railway between Tokyo and Kanagawa began.
== Births == * {{ill|Kashō|ja|嘉祥|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kashō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[850]] {{ill|May 10|ja|5月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Seiwa|ja|正和天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Seiwa|qq=}}, the 56th Emperor of Japan (died [[880]]). * [[Keichō]] 9th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1604]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 24|qq=}}) – {{ill|Matsudaira Naomoto|ja|松平直基|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Naomoto|qq=}}, lord of the Echizen, Ōno, Yamagata, and Himeji Domains (died [[1648]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1844]] {{ill|May 12|ja|5月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 12|qq=}}) – {{ill|Unii Ryūo|ja|雲井龍雄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Unii Ryūo|qq=}}, a military official and politician from the Yonezawa Domain (died [[1870]]). * 明治2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1869]] {{ill|May 6|ja|5月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 6|qq=}}) – {{ill|Inoue Junosuke|ja|井上準之助|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Inoue Junosuke|qq=}}, a politician (died [[1932]]). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1872]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Higuchi Ichiyō|ja|樋口一葉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Higuchi Ichiyō|qq=}}, a novelist and waka poet (died [[1896]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Taika|ja|大化|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taika|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[649]] {{ill|May 11|ja|5月11日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 11|qq=}}) – {{ill|Soga Kurayamada Ishikawa Maro|ja|蘇我倉山田石川麻呂|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga Kurayamada Ishikawa Maro|qq=}}, a noble and grandson of {{ill|Soga Umako|ja|蘇我馬子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga Umako|qq=}}. * {{ill|Meio|ja|明応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meio|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1499]] {{ill|May 5|ja|5月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Rennyo|ja|蓮如|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rennyo|qq=}}, the founder of Jōdo Shinshū (born [[1415]]).
